item.dc:creator: @Coldmedicine Coldmedicine
item.description:
@Coldmedicine wrote:

[quote=“Coldmedicine, post:1, topic:534827”][size=14pt]Okay, since you guys wouldnt stop messaging me, (over 250 messages) here it is again, but please stop asking for it…
Welcome to Aggroth V2,
I have released one more version of Aggroth, but it was really filled of bugs…
So due to lack of players, no time, and school starting again, i am hereby releasing my final version, PERHAPS in the future i might release one more version.

Features:
-Good combat
-Vine whip + special attack with a nice emote
-Glacor boots
-A perfect trivia system (editable)
-8 Ranks
-Custom nex, different styles of combat full animates, and a really cool area, made multiple too…
-Nomad a bit overpowered, new area and different styles of combat
-A nice snow texture pack
-All skills work, dungeoneering, farming, and a custom pking skill (credits for the pking skill to faris ofcourse)
-Fixed turmoil and soulsplit
-Custom special attack bar at home
-All leech prayers now
-Custom NPC’s, teleporting npcs and 2 shops in one npc
-All skillcapes (maybe i forgot one) in a custom shop
-Fixed pernix coif
-Tokhaar-kal or khal
-Sagittarian (full even bows)
-Ornate Katana
-Full completionist/milestone capes

And so much more to discover, pictures:

Custom login interfaces + background by Amy

Edgesville home with all npcs needed

A full custom tab (editable)

A full Pk points system + shop

A full leveling points system + shop
[img]http://puu.sh/48d3u.png[img]All%20660+%20npc%20dialogues[img]http://puu.sh/48d4H.jpg[img]

A full teleportation Npc

Full nex + emotes

Dashboard’s trivia

Teleportation interfaces

Full nomad 3 styles of combat

Fixed the ugly face

A full playerstore’s system + npc that explains and i fixed all dupes

Usually when you clicked “value” you would D/C and the other person could dupe meanwhile by buying the item, i fixed this.

Fixed total level, and the MakeOver mage glitch

Torva, pernix, virtus, all nex armours + effects (i think) ancient ceremonial and so much more

All apples fixed!

Links:
Cache Auto downloads
Source + client

Extra info:
There are several ranks added, and changed…

0 = Player
1 = Donator
2 = Super Donator
3 = Ultra Donator
4 = Dicer
5 = Helper
6 = Moderator
7 = Administrator
8 = Owner

If you need any help, dont bother asking me, unless you can pay, i have no more time for rs-ps atm.
Enjoy

Credits:
Austin Cadle, for my inspiration
Faris, maker of InsidiaX
Myself…
